metadata.name: risky business
metadata.description:
the lure of the money is what finally did it

commodities trading in miami led to his first visit to columbia...but not has last

the palmitas cartel originally contacted him to discuss risk mitigation from climate change on the farms that allegedly produced their high end coffee brand - "caina coffee"

it always starts with the first small compromise of your morals

first comes the money
then the power

manolo thought he was smart - but smarts won't get him out of this fvkn mess 

☠️
